author: alita85
content: I just launched the eip labelling feature. Basically, it will label a PR with as many labels that are relevant. Each file can only have one label type per, so if you have multiple files your PR can have multiple labels. But the associated label is mentioned in the bot's comment. Keep a look out for any times where something is assigned one thing when it shouldn't etc. There are lot of edges here, but the code is robust.
